  "title": "Napoleon Cake",
  "description": "The Napoleon Cake, also known as mille-feuille or custard slice, is a classic dessert made of multiple layers of thin puff pastry alternating with pastry cream. This confection is often topped with icing or powdered sugar and is recognized for its delicate, flaky layers and rich, creamy filling. The Napoleon Cake is a popular dessert in various cultures and is enjoyed for its combination of textures and flavors, blending crisp pastry with smooth, luscious cream.",
